00:06:07.559 --> 00:06:11.310
That's why after I write the first draft of
an article, I start editing it.

00:06:11.310 --> 00:06:12.909
Or I have someone else edit it.

00:06:12.909 --> 00:06:14.439
Whatever works in your business.

00:06:14.439 --> 00:06:15.439
The goal?

00:06:15.439 --> 00:06:17.520
To make it flow from start to finish.

00:06:17.520 --> 00:06:18.580
And that’s my process.

